headline: NRG Energy Stock Earns RS Rating Lift
summary: The Relative Strength (RS) Rating for NRG Energy stock headed into a new percentile Tuesday, as it got a lift from 68 to 78.    Can You Really Time The Stock Market?   This exclusive rating from Investor's Business Daily tracks price performance with a 1 (worst) to 99 (best) score.
